# Render Environment Variables Setup Guide
# ==========================================
# Add these as Environment Variables in Render Dashboard
# (Do NOT commit actual values to git)

# Required: OpenAI API Key
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Optional: Groq API Key (if using Groq instead)
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...

# Email Configuration (for Gmail)
EMAIL_SENDER=your-email@gmail.com
EMAIL_PASSWORD=your-app-password-here

# Optional: Secret for GitHub Actions authentication
DIGEST_SECRET=your-random-secret-here

# Render will automatically provide:
# - PORT (the port your app should listen on)
# - RENDER (set to "true")
# - RENDER_SERVICE_NAME
# - RENDER_INSTANCE_ID

# Your app URL will be set in GitHub Secrets as:
# RENDER_APP_URL=https://your-app-name.onrender.com
